_:N9ea9737a71d54e448bf6da854e5223f7 <http://schema.org/articleBody> "<div class=\"govspeak\"><h2 id=\"what-we-do\">What we do</h2>\n\n<p>The Health Equity in Health Protection Initiative supports UKHSA’s cross-cutting goal to deliver more equitable health outcomes. The initiative does this by helping UKHSA to build a strong foundation of data and evidence relevant to health equity in health protection. This includes understanding:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>the differential impact of health protection hazards on <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.england.nhs.uk/about/equality/equality-hub/national-healthcare-inequalities-improvement-programme/core20plus5/\">CORE20PLUS</a> and inclusion health groups</li>\n  <li>what interventions are most effective in reducing health inequalities in health protection</li>\n  <li>how communities experience and engage with health services</li>\n</ul>\n\n</div>" <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/jsonld> .
<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/health-equity-in-health-protection-initiative/about> <http://ogp.me/ns#title> "About us"@en <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/rdfa> .
